<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Alta de Zona</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #1a1a2e;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #0f3460;
        }
        header h1 {
            color: #00d4ff;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-right: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: #00d4ff;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #b0b0b0;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        form {
            background-color: #16213e;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        input[type="text"], input[type="number"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            background-color: #1f4068;
            color: #fff;
        }
        input[type="text"]::placeholder, input[type="number"]::placeholder {
            color: #b0b0b0;
        }
        input[type="submit"] {
            background-color: #00d4ff;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #00b2d4;
        }
        footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #0f3460;
            color: #fff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

{{>header }}

<div class="container">
    <h2>Alta de Nueva Zona</h2>
    <p>Introduce los detalles de la nueva zona que quieres dar de alta.</p>

    <form action="/alta-zona" method="POST">
        <label for="nombre">Nombre de la Zona:</label>
        <input type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" placeholder="Nombre de la zona" required>

        <label for="precio">Precio de la Zona (USD):</label>
        <input type="number" id="precio" name="precio" placeholder="Ejemplo: 1200" required>

        <label for="id">ID de la Zona:</label>
        <input type="text" id="id" name="id" placeholder="ID único de la zona" required>

        <input type="submit" value="Dar de alta">
    </form>
</div>

<footer>
    © 2024 Siemens. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
